66
00:06:15,290 --> 00:06:20,090
is to leave with the half piece of Bixi willingly given by someone from the Ji tribe.

67
00:06:21,730 --> 00:06:26,350
But the mortal has to come back within seven days.

68
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:30,620
