72
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:41,590
Jiuye can use this to carry items.

73
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,760
A big treasure!

74
00:08:39,610 --> 00:08:41,840
What big treasure is this?

75
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:11,530
I saw a living water guest.

76
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:13,670
Living water guest.

77
00:10:14,230 --> 00:10:16,370
Water guest, you're so lucky.

78
00:10:16,410 --> 00:10:17,490
You didn't die.

79
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:23,550
Who are you?

80
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:25,110
What do you want?

81
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:26,950
Listen.

82
00:10:27,070 --> 00:10:29,320
A long time ago, Grandma said

83
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:32,040
there will be a living water guest

84
00:10:32,060 --> 00:10:32,960
