85
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,960
coming to Sushui.

86
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:35,490
They don't believe it.

87
00:10:35,490 --> 00:10:36,660
Only I believe it.

88
00:10:36,690 --> 00:10:38,460
I knew you would definitely come.

89
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:39,130
Sushui?

90
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:42,040
