91
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:42,510
Let me have a look.

92
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,570
Don't come near me!

93
00:10:45,710 --> 00:10:46,170
This...

94
00:10:47,140 --> 00:10:48,340
This place is Sushui?

95
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:51,080
Yes.

96
00:10:55,210 --> 00:10:56,210
Where's my sword?

97
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,360
Are you looking for this?

98
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,160
No.

99
00:11:12,050 --> 00:11:13,280
What is a water guest?

100
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:15,000
A water guest?

101
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:16,720
A water guest is...

102
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:18,290
someone outside Sushui.

103
00:11:18,450 --> 00:11:20,310
A guest from the other side of the river.

104
00:11:20,310 --> 00:11:22,020
There were other guests before.

105
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:23,280
But they were all dead.

106
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:26,020
