111
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:37,770
Eat water guests?

112
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,140
Stop pretending.

113
00:11:40,310 --> 00:11:42,490
Aren't you Ji people monsters who eat raw meat,

114
00:11:42,490 --> 00:11:44,090
drink blood, do evil things,

115
00:11:44,110 --> 00:11:45,970
and bring disasters to the world?

116
00:11:51,530 --> 00:11:52,870
We are not close to each other.

117
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:53,620
Grandma said

118
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,970
we can't joke with someone not close to us.

119
00:11:56,930 --> 00:11:59,190
Why do you keep mentioning your grandma?

120
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,400
Who on earth is she?

121
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,280
Grandma?

122
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:03,070
