128
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:20,990
Here, I made some mushroom soup for you.

129
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:24,850
Drink something hot to warm your body.

130
00:12:24,850 --> 00:12:26,000
I finally got here.

131
00:12:26,650 --> 00:12:29,030
