132
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:31,360
how many soldiers they have as soon as possible,

133
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,530
so that it'll be convenient for us to attack them in the future

134
00:12:33,530 --> 00:12:34,630
to get Bixi successfully.

135
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:35,010
Here.

136
00:12:36,250 --> 00:12:36,910
Don't move.

137
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:40,390
